00:24:49,705 --> 00:24:52,665
I really like you, too.

539
00:24:52,708 --> 00:24:56,625
♪♪

540
00:24:59,759 --> 00:25:01,804
[Polly snorting]

541
00:25:01,848 --> 00:25:03,980
