582
00:26:50,478 --> 00:26:51,566
Oh, yeah.

583
00:26:51,610 --> 00:26:53,481
No, that took
a little getting used to.

584
00:26:53,524 --> 00:26:55,309
But it's cool,
you know?

585
00:26:55,352 --> 00:26:57,137
Yeah, it's pretty cool.

586
00:26:57,180 --> 00:26:59,792
I mean, you are
a big movie star.

587
00:26:59,835 --> 00:27:01,707
