665
00:30:51,588 --> 00:30:54,374
♪♪

666
00:30:54,417 --> 00:30:55,679
Wow.
I love it, Cody.

667
00:30:55,723 --> 00:30:57,072
Thank you.

668
00:30:59,074 --> 00:31:02,121
Just...

669
00:31:02,164 --> 00:31:04,079
