talk show thing.

762
00:35:47,319 --> 00:35:50,365
I couldn't get away.
I tried.

763
00:35:50,409 --> 00:35:53,977
Briley, I-I wish
I could've been here
for the whole show.

764
00:35:54,021 --> 00:35:55,892
I'm sorry.

765
00:35:55,936 --> 00:35:57,938
Hey, Cody,
another talk show

766
00:35:57,981 --> 00:35:59,244
