for next week.

767
00:35:59,287 --> 00:36:00,897
Yeah, yeah, that's good.

768
00:36:00,941 --> 00:36:02,334
Okay.
[whispering] Sorry.

769
00:36:04,597 --> 00:36:06,207
[sighs]

770
