00:42:31,592 --> 00:42:34,421
And then pour it in.

867
00:42:34,464 --> 00:42:35,553
Whoo!

868
00:42:35,596 --> 00:42:36,466
[both chuckling]

869
00:42:36,510 --> 00:42:38,077
Stir, stir, stir,
stir, stir!

