966
00:46:51,156 --> 00:46:52,548
[man]
That's a cut, everyone!

967
00:46:52,592 --> 00:46:53,593
Sorry.

968
00:46:53,636 --> 00:46:55,682
[man]
Stand by!

969
00:46:55,725 --> 00:46:59,164
