999
00:48:27,687 --> 00:48:29,123
I'll see you tomorrow,
okay?

1000
00:48:29,167 --> 00:48:30,864
Get some rest.

1001
00:48:30,908 --> 00:48:32,170
I will.

1002
00:48:32,213 --> 00:48:33,562
Thanks, Ed.
Have a good night.

1003
00:48:33,606 --> 00:48:34,999
[Ed]
You too, buddy.

1004
00:48:37,784 --> 00:48:39,525
Cody, man,
great work today.

1005
00:48:39,568 --> 00:48:41,788
