a little bit back there.

1006
00:48:41,831 --> 00:48:42,528
[chuckles]

1007
00:48:42,571 --> 00:48:43,746
Um, okay, look.

1008
00:48:43,790 --> 00:48:45,705
I know it's a lot,
but the guys at the studio

1009
00:48:45,748 --> 00:48:47,489
