Little tired.

1024
00:49:13,907 --> 00:49:16,997
Okay, yeah.
Uh, get some rest.

1025
00:49:17,041 --> 00:49:18,607
We can't have you
burning out, right?

1026
00:49:18,651 --> 00:49:19,478
