[door opens]

1058
00:50:34,727 --> 00:50:38,165
[phone line trilling]

1059
00:50:38,209 --> 00:50:39,297
Hello?

1060
00:50:39,340 --> 00:50:40,515
[woman on phone]
Hello?

1061
00:50:40,559 --> 00:50:41,951
Yeah, hi.
It's Briley Williams.

1062
00:50:41,995 --> 00:50:43,518
Hey, Briley.
